This will remove members from an existing multi-sig account

## Import

```ts
import { BaseSignerClient } from "@account-kit/signer";
```

## Parameters

### orgId

`string`
orgId of the multi-sig to remove members from

### members

`Address[]`
the addresses of the members to remove
